{"tid":219413,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"亞洲足協起訴廣州恒大","createTime":"2017-04-27T08:07:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-28T03:13:10.000Z","uid":47272,"like":200,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"eb5e0ad1e8e1f1b5f864f52a8e2122d2f44c5a8b","tid":219413,"uid":47272,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T08:07:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170427&amp;s=7032049&amp;a=56621216\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170427%26s%3D7032049%26a%3D56621216&d=pZTDRaRh7CFw%2FURiZY0DNZ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=ab1b900b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170427%26s%3D7032049%26a%3D56621216&h=a570f86f\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170427&amp;s=7032049&amp;a=56621216</a><br />\n亞洲足協（AFC）周四發表聲明，正式起訴三間球會違反AFC的紀律和道德守則，當中包括周二在亞洲聯賽冠軍盃G組分組賽6:0大勝東方龍獅的中超球隊廣州恒大。<br />\n<br />\n恒大周二在亞冠盃G組作客大勝東方的分組賽，有球迷在比賽末段於旺角場作客球迷區展示「殲英犬 滅港毒」的標語，儘管有關動作為時只有數十秒，橫額即馬上被收起，但由於此類標語帶有政治意味，明顯是違反了亞洲足協的守則。"},{"pid":"e044159b328ff4a250c46f0ee54f5b61339576ea","tid":219413,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T08:14:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"330f7ead1ac95f20193c0148a206cd277014db90","tid":219413,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T08:15:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f13af2993f55cb9a05d3aa3753d6d17173a67b2","tid":219413,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T08:16:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9138809dedb5d37e992ca63d3aae74ad43bdd79a","tid":219413,"uid":102056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T08:19:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"74f14a87d4b3af85ef7005fd74df315e224710bf","tid":219413,"uid":91227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T08:19:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d22ee0a3345bc11477c090540272f250ae32450","tid":219413,"uid":76488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T08:20:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1f69c2501c52d7d92ae6d5f22860736d0f8bd8af","tid":219413,"uid":15935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T08:21:37.000Z","msg":"會罰啲咩？"},{"pid":"e71e4e8d725c5b5ca503e8bdbdb0035f54cba816","tid":219413,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T08:24:36.000Z","msg":"強國水準？ 中、港足球大戰 中國球迷大罵「X你老母」<br />\n<br />\n2017-04-27 11:05<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕港超「東方龍獅」昨日在主場迎戰中超「廣州恒大」，最終以0：6落敗。但過程中「廣州恒大」球迷在場內高舉政治標語，甚至集體向香港球迷飆髒話，「東方龍獅」已就此事向官方反映。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，兩支球隊昨日於香港旺角球場對戰，雖然「恒大」以6分之差大勝對手，但有球迷在場內舉出「殲英犬、滅港毒」的標語，還集體向港人大聲怒罵「X你老母」、「漢奸」、「走狗」等不雅文字。<br />\n<br />\n這樣的行為獲得不少中國網友的讚賞，認為是在教「港燦」（對港人的貶稱）怎麼做人，還大讚飆髒話的舉動充滿「正義感」。有在場人士指出，中國球迷的舉動是因為場內有港人噓中國國歌、舉香港旗。<br />\n<br />\n由於比賽進行中出現政治、種族歧視標語，「東方龍獅」已在當下拍照存證，賽後向香港足總及亞洲足協委派的場監匯報，希望官方能公正調查此事並做出回應。<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2049267\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2049267&d=pZTDRaRh7CFw%2FURiZY0DNZ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=0b483dbf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2049267&h=7ff6a92d\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2049267</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/1NkaGFsoYsw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F1NkaGFsoYsw&d=pZTDRaRh7CFw%2FURiZY0DNZ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=9e4c2141\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/1NkaGFsoYsw</a>"},{"pid":"131fde40b2a487b4fdb5a4b1e2a4a5d3d970cfd9","tid":219413,"uid":6799